                  <hi rendition="#g">Herders Brief:</hi> an J. P.<lb/>IV. Abt., IV, Nr. 158. <hi rendition="#rkd">29–31</hi> Vgl. <hi rendition="#b">10</hi>, <hi rendition="#rkd">18</hi>f. <hi rendition="#rkd">31</hi>ff. Otto hatte Proben
